        <updateDate>2021-11-18T20:14:37Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Renewable Energy Investment Act</strong></p> <p>This bill allows taxpayers, including certain pass-thru entities such as partnerships and S corporations, to elect to receive tax excludable payments in lieu of amounts attributable to the tax credits for energy property and for electricity produced from certain renewable resources.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
